dmca.title: TV DMCA (Copyright) Complaint to Google: Android Market

works.description:
With over 10 million active players on  
Facebook worldwide Diamond Dash is a well known social game created and  
developed by wooga GmbH. Moreover, "Diamond Dash" is copyrighted by wooga 

GmbH. We believe the two applications mentioned are making use of our  
popularity, brand and concept to distribute and sell their games. We also 

consider that users might be led to believe the apps below are made and  
developed by wooga GmbH when, in fact, we have no association whatsoever  
with the developer. Some of the graphical elements (as well as colors) of 

the apps are also similar to those designed and used by wooga GmbH in our 

application Diamond Dash:
